    "description": "General-purpose N-channel depletion-mode junction FET for audio and low-frequency small-signal amplifier applications. Its two defining specs are the zero-gate-voltage drain (saturation) current IDSS (1 to 5 mA) and the gate-source cutoff voltage VGS(off) (-0.5 to -6.0 V). JEDEC-registered part in the 2N5457/58/59 family.",
